reviewText: One of the best DVD's I have EVER bought... Anointed music.

Good Worship music from Brazil, Jazz, Funk, Rock mixed. Excellent musicians like the guitarist Cacau Santos.
The ambiance in the concert is great!
In portuguese.
Is The best Christian lbum. I recomended 100%. If you like Christian music this Is for you,!, this DVD come with subtitule in English and Spanish
